high_descs: Turn around, move forward a little and turn right. Reach the tissuebox.
Turn around, go straight ahead. Turn right. Reach the wall. Turn right. Lower the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Find a TissueBox, light a DeskLamp.

high_descs: Walk around the bed to the tissuebox at the side of the bed, near the head of the bed.
Take the tissuebox of the box and close the box.
Walk around the desk to the side with the desklamp.
Turn on the desklamp that is on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Look at the TissueBox with the DeskLamp light.

high_descs: Turn left and walk few steps to reach the desk on the left side
Take a tissue box which is kept in the cardboard box that is kept in the floor next to desk
Turn back and walk few steps and turn right to reach the desk lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the tissue box by the light of a desk lamp.
